sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / Dashboard
    participant Router as OpenShift Router<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Proxy as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS (service-ca)
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant APIServer as API Server<br/>8888/TCP REST<br/>8887/TCP gRPC
    participant MariaDB as MariaDB<br/>3306/TCP MySQL
    participant S3 as S3 Object Store<br/>443/9000 TCP
    participant WFCtrl as Workflow Controller<br/>(Argo)
    participant TaskPod as Pipeline Task Pod
    participant MLMD as MLMD gRPC Server<br/>8080/TCP gRPC
    participant PersAgent as Persistence Agent

    Note over User,PersAgent: Flow 1: Pipeline Run Submission (External User)
    User->>Router: POST /apis/v1beta1/runs<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+
    Router->>Proxy: Reencrypt TLS<br/>HTTPS/8443
    Proxy->>K8sAPI: SubjectAccessReview<br/>HTTPS/443, SA token
    K8sAPI-->>Proxy: Authorized
    Proxy->>APIServer: Forward request<br/>HTTPS/8888, TLS (service-ca)
    APIServer->>MariaDB: Store pipeline run<br/>MySQL/3306, TLS, user/pass
    MariaDB-->>APIServer: Stored
    APIServer->>S3: Upload pipeline spec<br/>HTTPS/443, AccessKey/SecretKey
    S3-->>APIServer: Uploaded
    APIServer->>K8sAPI: Create Workflow CR<br/>HTTPS/443, SA token
    K8sAPI-->>APIServer: Created
    APIServer-->>Proxy: 200 OK
    Proxy-->>Router: Response
    Router-->>User: JSON Response

    Note over User,PersAgent: Flow 2: Pipeline Execution (Argo Workflow)
    WFCtrl->>K8sAPI: Watch Workflow CRs<br/>HTTPS/443, SA token
    K8sAPI-->>WFCtrl: Workflow event
    WFCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create Task Pod<br/>HTTPS/443, SA token
    K8sAPI-->>WFCtrl: Pod created
    TaskPod->>APIServer: Get pipeline params<br/>HTTPS/8888, TLS (service-ca)
    APIServer-->>TaskPod: Parameters
    TaskPod->>S3: Read/Write artifacts<br/>HTTPS/443, AccessKey/SecretKey
    S3-->>TaskPod: Artifacts
    TaskPod->>MLMD: Log execution metadata<br/>gRPC/8080, TLS (service-ca)
    MLMD-->>TaskPod: Logged
    TaskPod->>K8sAPI: Report status<br/>HTTPS/443, SA token

    Note over User,PersAgent: Flow 3: Status Synchronization
    PersAgent->>K8sAPI: Watch Workflow status<br/>HTTPS/443, SA token
    K8sAPI-->>PersAgent: Status update
    PersAgent->>APIServer: Update run status<br/>HTTPS/8888, TLS (service-ca)
    APIServer->>MariaDB: Persist status<br/>MySQL/3306, TLS
    MariaDB-->>APIServer: Stored

    Note over User,PersAgent: Flow 3: DSPO Reconciliation
    Note right of K8sAPI: DSPO Controller watches DSPA CRs
    K8sAPI-->>K8sAPI: DSPA CR change detected
    K8sAPI->>MariaDB: Health check<br/>MySQL/3306
    MariaDB-->>K8sAPI: Healthy
    K8sAPI->>S3: Health check<br/>HTTPS/443
    S3-->>K8sAPI: Healthy
    K8sAPI->>K8sAPI: Apply component templates<br/>(Deployments, Services, Routes, NetworkPolicies)
